description.en-us: Battle Force 5 (formerly BattleRacers ) was an animated TV series created by Nelvana Limited and Nerd Corps. in partnership with Mattel. The earliest known commercial for this series aired on 25 June 2009. Shortly after, a preview consisting of two episodes aired on Cartoon Network in the United States on 24 August 2009. The series then made its official debut on 29 August 2009.
